                    </p>
                    <p>
                        We do not share your data with third parties. All operations are for demonstration purposes within this project.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-muted small">
                        Built with <strong>ASP.NET Core MVC</strong> and <strong>Bootstrap</strong> for educational purposes.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
